.DT
add_random_chat
Disk World creator help
add_random_chat

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_random_chat -  This method is to add to the list of random chats that can be added to specific room types.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_random_chat(string types,
string * chats)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^types%^RESET%^ - the string of ASCII character type(s) that this desc could apply to
%^BOLD%^chats%^RESET%^ - an array of chats to add. Usual add_chat format.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is to add to the list of random chats that can be added to
specific room types. A specific random sequence is used so that the randoms
won't vary over time.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_random_desc_limit, set_random_chat_limit, add_random_chat

.EP

